c: 11
v: 81
t: "(Izithunywa) zathi, “Oh! Lothi ngempela thina siyizithunywa zeNkosi yakho abasoze bafinyelela kuwena ngakho-ke hamba nomndeni wakho ngengxenye yobusuku, phakathi kwenu makungabibikho ngisho noyedwa ozobheka emumva ngaphandle konkosikazi wakho ngempela (unkosikazi wakho) uyovelelwa ilokho okuyobavelela, ngempela isithembiso sabo sisekuseni, ngakube akusondele yini ukusa na"